high_descs: Pick up the pan from the island.
Bring the pan to the fridge.
Chill the pan in the fridge.
Bring the chilled pan to the stove.
Put the chilled pan on the left of the stove.
anns.task_desc: Put a chilled pan on the stove.

high_descs: Walk forward and right around to the other side of the kitchen island
Pick up the square pan from the kitchen island
Turn around and walk to the fridge
Put the pan on the top left fridge shelf then remove it
Turn right and walk over to the stove
Put the pan on the front left stove burner
anns.task_desc: Put the chilled pan on the stove

high_descs: Go straight, turn right, then turn right to face the table.
Pick up the pan nearest to you on the table.
Turn around and approach the fridge.
Chill the pan in the fridge.
Turn around, then go left to the stove.
Place the pan on the bottom left corner of the stove.
anns.task_desc: Put a chilled pan on the stove.
